.el .ds Aq '
.TH runs 1  "runs " 
.SH NAME
runs \- Show recent task execution history
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBruns\fR [\fB\-\-skill\fR] [\fB\-\-limit\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Show recent task execution history.
.PP
Displays the results of past task executions, including status, timestamps, and output previews.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-skill\fR \fI<NAME>\fR
Filter runs by task (skill) name
.TP
\fB\-\-limit\fR \fI<N>\fR [default: 20]
Maximum number of runs to display
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
